</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA041394-0019 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 031680 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
April 13, 1994, Wednesday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
View; Part E; Page 3; Column 5; View Desk 
</P>
