 Joe Louis and Sugar Ray Robinson died on April 12 -- Louis in 1981 and 
Robinson in 1989. . . . Stuntmen from the Wild, Wild, Wild West Show will teach 
Evander Holyfield and Michael Moorer how to take a punch during a news 
