FOR THE RECORD 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Pacific Telesis stock -- The Stock Market Leaders and Laggards chart Monday 
listed Pacific Telesis as the communications stock with the greatest loss in 
value during the previous week. Although the stock lost value, stockholders 
suffered no overall loss because they also received AirTouch stock as part of a 
spinoff of the company's wireless business. 
</P>
