<TEXT>
<P>
 Nate Laufer pitched a no-hitter and struck out 19 in L.A. Baptist High's 26-1 
victory over Marshall on Tuesday in an Alpha League baseball game at L.A. 
Baptist. 
</P>
<P>
 Laufer (3-2), who faced four batters over the minimum, threw 122 pitches, 83 
for strikes. 
</P>
<P>
