<HEADLINE>
<P>
PREP VOLLEYBALL ROUNDUP 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 In another Sea View League match: 
</P>
<P>
 Irvine 3 University 2 -- Blair Eldridge had 17 kills for Irvine (5-3, 4-3), 
which won, 15-7, 15-10, 10-15, 15-17, 15-13. 
</P>
<P>
 In the Century League: 
</P>
<P>
