Florida for unprofessional conduct. License revoked in Florida for prescribing 
controlled substances to six people who were not his patients, including his 
wife. Failed to keep medical records of his course of treatment of his wife. 
Revocation of license stayed; three years probation. Effective June 19, 1993. 
</P>
