<DOCNO> LA041394-0238 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 031899 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
April 13, 1994, Wednesday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Part A; Page 1; Column 1; National Desk 
