 Sorensen has no money or identification and was last seen wearing jeans, a 
short-sleeved checkered polo shirt, a white or blue sweat shirt and white 
athletic shoes, Martini said. He is a quiet man who has trouble answering 
complex questions, but will probably respond if asked if his name is John 
Sorensen. 
